title: Omoide no Mânî
overview: Due to 12 y.o. Anna's asthma, she's sent to stay with relatives of her guardian in the Japanese countryside. She likes to be alone, sketching. She befriends Marnie. Who is the mysterious, blonde Marnie.

title: Coraline
overview: An adventurous 11-year-old girl finds another world that is a strangely idealized version of her frustrating home, but it has sinister secrets.

title: Mimi wo sumaseba
overview: A love story between a girl who loves reading books, and a boy who has previously checked out all of the library books she chooses.

title: Majo no takkyûbin
overview: A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.

title: Rupan sansei: Kariosutoro no shiro
overview: A dashing thief, his gang of desperadoes and an intrepid policeman struggle to free a princess from an evil count's clutches, and learn the hidden secret to a fabulous treasure that she holds part of a key to.

title: Kaguyahime no monogatari
overview: Found inside a shining stalk of bamboo by an old bamboo cutter and his wife, a tiny girl grows rapidly into an exquisite young lady. The mysterious young princess enthralls all who encounter her, but ultimately she must confront her fate, the punishment for her crime.

title: Tonari no Totoro
overview: When two girls move to the country to be near their ailing mother, they have adventures with the wondrous forest spirits who live nearby.

title: The Kid
overview: The Tramp cares for an abandoned child, but events put that relationship in jeopardy.

title: Hotaru no haka
overview: A young boy and his little sister struggle to survive in Japan during World War II.

title: Le Petit Prince
overview: A little girl lives in a very grown-up world with her mother, who tries to prepare her for it. Her neighbor, the Aviator, introduces the girl to an extraordinary world where anything is possible, the world of the Little Prince.

title: Ôkami kodomo no Ame to Yuki
overview: After her werewolf lover unexpectedly dies in an accident while hunting for food for their children, a young woman must find ways to raise the werewolf son and daughter that she had with him while keeping their trait hidden from society.

title: Hauru no ugoku shiro
overview: When an unconfident young woman is cursed with an old body by a spiteful witch, her only chance of breaking the spell lies with a self-indulgent yet insecure young wizard and his companions in his legged, walking castle.

title: Tenkû no shiro Rapyuta
overview: A young boy and a girl with a magic crystal must race against pirates and foreign agents in a search for a legendary floating castle.

title: Kimi no na wa.
overview: Two strangers find themselves linked in a bizarre way. When a connection forms, will distance be the only thing to keep them apart?

title: WALL·E
overview: In the distant future, a small waste-collecting robot inadvertently embarks on a space journey that will ultimately decide the fate of mankind.

title: The Little Mermaid
overview: A mermaid princess makes a Faustian bargain in an attempt to become human and win a prince's love.

title: Hachi: A Dog's Tale
overview: A college professor bonds with an abandoned dog he takes into his home.

title: Sen to Chihiro no kamikakushi
overview: During her family's move to the suburbs, a sullen 10-year-old girl wanders into a world ruled by gods, witches, and spirits, and where humans are changed into beasts.

title: The Sandlot
overview: In the summer of 1962, a new kid in town is taken under the wing of a young baseball prodigy and his rowdy team, resulting in many adventures.

title: The Secret of Kells
overview: A young boy in a remote medieval outpost under siege from barbarian raids is beckoned to adventure when a celebrated master illuminator arrives with an ancient book, brimming with secret wisdom and powers.
